{
  "title": "Vibrant Tender Algerian Potato Tagine",
  "description": "A funky and tender Algerian dish featuring russet potatoes, perfect for a sick day, made with ayurvedic-sattvic-friendly ingredients.",
  "cuisine": "Algerian",
